00:00:13.713 --> 00:00:15.581
probably find her birth father-

00:00:15.648 --> 00:00:16.949
and she called me up one night-

00:00:17.049 --> 00:00:20.653
She told me that she thought
she found him.

00:00:22.255 --> 00:00:23.689
You do look like him!

00:00:23.856 --> 00:00:24.791
We were just like- 

00:00:24.791 --> 00:00:26.925
"That's him. That's him."

