00:00:33.299 --> 00:00:36.769
out of three boys and three
girls in the family

00:00:36.869 --> 00:00:39.138
that I was unable to have kids.

00:00:39.205 --> 00:00:40.606
It was just a miracle.

00:00:40.773 --> 00:00:43.275
<i>Woman</i>: Sandy and his brother Jay

00:00:43.342 --> 00:00:44.744
knew where Deborah lived-

00:00:44.811 --> 00:00:47.180
and said "Wanna go drive by?"

00:00:47.247 --> 00:00:49.582
And so we thought-

00:00:49.648 --> 00:00:51.016
"Ok."

00:00:51.283 --> 00:00:52.718
Angela right away said 

00:00:52.852 --> 00:00:55.121
"Deborah I think you might be my
birth mother."

00:00:55.388 --> 00:00:57.556
<i> Man</i>: And I could just hear
Deborah say

00:00:57.556 --> 00:00:59.658
"I'm not the person you're 
looking for."

00:00:59.758 --> 00:01:01.260
<i>Woman</i>: It was just really sad.

00:01:01.460 --> 00:01:03.730
I just felt so bad for her.

00:01:04.030 --> 00:01:12.104
♪♪

00:01:12.304 --> 00:01:14.207
Deborah may be the one
person on this world

00:01:14.273 --> 00:01:16.976
that I will not be able to 
figure out.

00:01:17.343 --> 00:01:23.916
♪♪

00:01:24.283 --> 00:01:26.786
My blood and your blood are
the same.

00:01:27.119 --> 00:01:29.255
♪♪

